Definition: in accordance with what is appropriate or suitable for the circumstances
Example: he was appropriately dressed; If you don't behave properly, you'll have to leave!; I met the junior senator from Illinois and I was duly impressed
Synonyms: inappropriately, adj, all, appropriate, suitably, unsuitably, fit, suitable, fittingly, befittingly, befitting, fitly, properly, proper, duly, in, accordance, with, what, is, or, for, the, circumstances, he, was, dressed, If, you, don, t, behave, ll, have, to, leave, I, met, junior, senator, from, Illinois, and, impressed
Category: adv.all
